{"tid":2215553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"售CSi罩稱廣州產 藥房東主罰款","createTime":"2020-09-24T05:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T09:48:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cea957ae41bf10f3e0f4b425990c94f3bb9e3b45","tid":2215553,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/JRDFW5MOZZH2FAGB3NCX7HIVFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FJRDFW5MOZZH2FAGB3NCX7HIVFE%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=55145b88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FJRDFW5MOZZH2FAGB3NCX7HIVFE%2F&h=31493c1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/JRDFW5MOZZH2FAGB3NCX7HIVFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n售CSi罩稱廣州產 藥房東主罰款<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年武漢肺炎疫情爆發初期，懲教署生產的CSi口罩不時在坊間出現。海關1月底派員到灣仔一間藥房「放蛇」，以60元購入10個CSi口罩，當時東主向卧底訛稱口罩在廣州生產。涉案東主昨承認違反《商品說明條例》，求情稱因一時疏忽才犯案，日後不會再犯。裁判官指涉案口罩數量不多，而且是真口罩，判被告罰款2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：按政府要求推優惠 不准涉及購物  百佳搞3,200萬抽獎 區議員：減價最實際<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XQxCsrwBA-RUzdJ3vl0aBoWjD_E=/2071x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KLI7AXTYNJG3LGE6Y5FFQKKJEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXQxCsrwBA-RUzdJ3vl0aBoWjD_E%3D%2F2071x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKLI7AXTYNJG3LGE6Y5FFQKKJEA.jpg&h=9b1684c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告白國機違反《商品說明條例》，被判罰款2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官囑咐：以後小心啲<br />\n<br />\n被告白國機（42歲）面對一項供應已應用虛假商品說明的貨品罪。暫委裁判官陳志輝昨判刑後囑咐被告「以後自己小心啲」，搞清楚貨品來源地。陳官應控方申請，將涉案口罩歸還海關。<br />\n<br />\n案情指今年1月31日，海關卧底在灣仔金烽參茸藥行購入兩包共10個CSi口罩。被。。。。。。。。。。。懲教主任證實涉案口罩是在羅湖懲教所生產。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2006/20"},{"pid":"8a763073684100f8adad442cb5d65551eb7d7932","tid":2215553,"uid":54502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"罰款2,000元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又破大案啦"},{"pid":"c89092a0062add25f368da4b65ca88910ba9da6a","tid":2215553,"uid":77196,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁邊個供貨俾佢呀，拉散貨唔拉供貨有撚用咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9dd3a0ee06ebb03a413ffb2e1d8cb09936a4a4","tid":2215553,"uid":211466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"下?!<br />\n冇拿?<br />\n背後成個犯罪集團呢"},{"pid":"f5df463f3db23463ceecf1e731939f104b41fb4c","tid":2215553,"uid":64073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:36:40.000Z","msg":"賣老鼠貨告呢條罪？"},{"pid":"5232bd93ae49033b1c64adead8262eb7c60489b8","tid":2215553,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:30:52.000Z","msg":"歸還海關？懲教做既係都還懲教啦，如果係藥房東主合法取得就歸還東主啦，點解歸還海關？證實批貨係海關流出？"},{"pid":"dc7e6487b82b914bfd0547a3a14b84cc0079f32e","tid":2215553,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"乜CSI三隻字你匪教處專用個咩？"},{"pid":"d5c8fb47a8ebc1d68580b872f8e088afbb724789","tid":2215553,"uid":314604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:48:04.000Z","msg":"以後小心啲？個官咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}